# Table Layout Standards

## Font Size Standards
All table components must maintain consistent font sizes:

```css
/* Table data - equivalent to 11pt */
.table-cell-fixed {
  font-size: 14px !important;
  line-height: 1.2 !important;
}

/* Table headers - equivalent to 11pt */
.table-header-fixed {
  font-size: 14px !important;
  font-weight: 600 !important;
  line-height: 1.2 !important;
}

/* Card content - equivalent to 12pt */
.card-content-fixed {
  font-size: 16px !important;
  line-height: 1.3 !important;
}

/* Card titles - equivalent to 13.5pt */
.card-title-fixed {
  font-size: 18px !important;
  font-weight: 700 !important;
  line-height: 1.3 !important;
}
```

## Dynamic Table Width
Tables must resize dynamically based on column count to prevent internal scrolling:

```typescript
// Table container width formula
const tableWidth = Math.max(400, 100 + (visibleColumns.length * 95));

// Individual column minimum widths
const columnMinWidths = {
  dateColumn: 'min-w-[80px]',
  dataColumn: 'min-w-[85px]'
};
```

## Table Cell Structure
All table cells must use fixed font classes and proper spacing:

```tsx
<TableHead className="text-center table-header-fixed px-3 whitespace-nowrap min-w-[85px]">
  {getColumnLabel(column)}
</TableHead>

<TableCell className="font-mono table-cell-fixed text-center py-2 px-3 whitespace-nowrap min-w-[85px]">
  {formattedValue}
</TableCell>
```

## Card Content Structure
Card headers and content must use fixed font classes:

```tsx
<CardTitle className="card-title-fixed mb-3 truncate">
  {group.game}
</CardTitle>
<div className="card-content-fixed text-muted-foreground space-y-2">
  {/* Content with 12pt font */}
</div>
```

## Critical Requirements
- ✅ NO internal table scrolling - tables must expand to fit all columns
- ✅ Font sizes NEVER change regardless of column count
- ✅ Use CSS classes with `!important` to prevent overrides
- ✅ Minimum column widths must be respected
- ✅ Proper padding and spacing for readability